<i>Here's Hank Williams' hit tune,</i>
<i>"Cold, Cold Heart."</i>

4
00:02:42,496 --> 00:02:44,623
You ain't ever gonna
amount to nothing.

5
00:02:44,831 --> 00:02:48,752
